And I went through a series of things,

00:17:01.720 --> 00:17:03.200
I'm not gonna do that this morning,

00:17:03.200 --> 00:17:06.000
of things that He said that have come to pass

00:17:06.020 --> 00:17:09.140
and things that He has said that have not yet come to pass

00:17:09.140 --> 00:17:11.020
but we have the confidence and the faith

00:17:11.020 --> 00:17:14.700
knowing that He always does what He says He will do

00:17:14.700 --> 00:17:16.899
and how we can rejoice in that.

00:17:16.899 --> 00:17:19.739
Notice here He says, the angel,

00:17:19.739 --> 00:17:22.500
He says He is not here, He is risen, as He said.

00:17:22.500 --> 00:17:26.339
Turn back a few pages to Matthew chapter number 16.

00:17:26.339 --> 00:17:27.500
Matthew chapter number 16

00:17:27.500 --> 00:17:29.360
is a wonderful passage of scripture,

00:17:29.360 --> 00:17:31.339
one in which I love going to

00:17:31.339 --> 00:17:33.779
and reading the passage of scripture.

00:17:33.800 --> 00:17:37.239
There's a great truth, many great truths in this passage.

00:17:37.239 --> 00:17:39.600
One wonderful promise that we often quote

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.959
