Here in Matthew 16 is when He began.

00:21:27.459 --> 00:21:29.259
It says from that time forth

00:21:29.259 --> 00:21:32.039
began Jesus to show unto His disciples

00:21:32.039 --> 00:21:33.279
all of these things

00:21:33.279 --> 00:21:35.979
