00:22:00.579 --> 00:22:01.959
for a lengthy period of time

00:22:01.959 --> 00:22:05.139
during His earthly ministry.

00:22:05.139 --> 00:22:07.059
And this caused sorrow.

00:22:07.059 --> 00:22:09.259
You can look at the sister passage

00:22:09.259 --> 00:22:11.299
