00:22:11.299 --> 00:22:12.699
and understand how Jesus

00:22:12.699 --> 00:22:15.059
was revealing these things to His disciples.

00:22:15.059 --> 00:22:16.539
And it was there in chapter 14

00:22:16.539 --> 00:22:18.839
when He says, let not your heart be troubled.

00:22:18.839 --> 00:22:20.479
They were saddened by that

00:22:20.479 --> 00:22:21.579
which they had heard,

00:22:21.579 --> 00:22:24.359
but we understand that this is the plan of God.

00:22:24.359 --> 00:22:25.639
Throughout the book of John,

00:22:25.659 --> 00:22:28.759
we read this reference with regard to the hour.

00:22:28.759 --> 00:22:30.659
Jesus says in John 2,

00:22:30.659 --> 00:22:33.499
the first miracle there at Cana,

00:22:33.499 --> 00:22:34.659
the marriage,

00:22:34.659 --> 00:22:37.699
