00:22:49.459 --> 00:22:50.739
It was time.

00:22:50.739 --> 00:22:54.079
See, Jesus understood the plan of redemption.

00:22:54.079 --> 00:22:56.819
And we sing often this song.

00:22:56.819 --> 00:23:00.059
He was born to die.

00:23:00.059 --> 00:23:02.719
Why? So that man could be reconciled.

00:23:02.719 --> 00:23:05.859
So that we could be redeemed.

00:23:05.859 --> 00:23:07.859
Jesus was showing His disciples.

00:23:07.859 --> 00:23:09.579
He was teaching His disciples

00:23:09.579 --> 00:23:11.019
that yes, He would be killed,

00:23:11.019 --> 00:23:12.899
but that He would be raised again

00:23:12.899 --> 00:23:13.859
on the third day.

00:23:13.859 --> 00:23:16.059
Notice in chapter 20 here

00:23:16.059 --> 00:23:17.619
of the book of Matthew.

