00:23:24.619 --> 00:23:26.799
took the twelve disciples apart in the way

00:23:26.799 --> 00:23:28.259
and said unto them,

00:23:28.259 --> 00:23:30.699
Behold, we go up to Jerusalem

00:23:30.699 --> 00:23:32.339
and the Son of Man shall be betrayed

00:23:32.339 --> 00:23:33.579
unto the chief priests

00:23:33.579 --> 00:23:34.979
and unto the scribes,

00:23:34.979 --> 00:23:37.219
